ORA Reactome analysis by clusterProfiler by symbol identifiers.

doRA.Rd

ORA Reactome analysis by clusterProfiler by symbol identifiers.

Usage

doRA(GS, PVal = 0.01, QVal = 0.05, Organism = "human", OrgDB = org.Hs.eg.db)

Arguments

GS

Gene Symbols for enrichment analysis. NOT ENSEMBL ID.

PVal

P adjusted value cut off, default 0.01

QVal

qvalue cut off, default 0.05

Organism

one of "human", "rat", "mouse", "celegans", "yeast", "zebrafish", "fly".

OrgDB

default as org.Hs.eg.db

Value

An enrichment result generated by clusterProfiler.

Zhiming Ye
